"'''Polarization: Revelations'''" is a roleplaying-game adventure in year five of the [[Living Force (roleplaying campaign)|Living Force]] campaign. It is the second adventure of the [[Polarization trilogy]] and was written by [[Margaret van Poelgeest-Heintz|Margaret Heintz]] and edited by [[Ronald A. Heintz|Ron Heintz]].

==Opening crawl==
''As the mysterious crime lord is revealed and the personal motives exposed the violence steps up as Nirama realizes that he's fighting not only for his empire, but for his life.''

